  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a failed love confession, Aoi Takamatsu dropped out of school and became a shut-in. It was one of these rare days where he left his home to go shopping. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blinded by the sun on this warm summer day he looked up to the sky and saw a naked girl falling from the sky?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This was the moment his boring life changed forever...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Different endings, depending on your choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Original Anime Art and Soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Available for Windows, Mac and Linux</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get an exclusive digital dakimakura, only available on steam!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
